---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { social } from '../data/social';
---

<Base title="About" activePage="about" description="Purple Directive builds compliance-grade software and operations infrastructure for clinical research. Meet the founder behind the work.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero hero">
    <p class="about-tagline">About Us</p>
    <h1>We Build What Clinical Research<br/>Operations Actually Need</h1>
    <p class="about-subtitle">
      Purple Directive is a consultancy that builds compliance-grade software and
      operations infrastructure for sponsors, CROs, and research sites. We work at
      the intersection of clinical research and technology — where regulatory rigor
      meets modern engineering.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin story — split -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-split">
      <div class="about-split-left">
        <h2>How We Got Here</h2>
        <p>
          Purple Directive started where most small research sites start: active
          studies, borrowed SOPs, and commercial platforms sized for organizations
          ten times as large. The tools that existed were either too expensive, too
          rigid, or both — built for 500-person CROs with dedicated IT, not for
          coordinators who also handle regulatory submissions and study close-out
          in the same week.
        </p>
        <p>
          So we started building. SOPs aligned to ICH E6(R2/R3), written to cover
          the full study lifecycle without the filler. A clinical trial management
          system with a real audit trail and the workflows that coordinators
          actually use. Each tool was built because we needed it ourselves —
          developed during active work on FDA-regulated studies at a 21-hospital
          US academic health system. If it didn't hold up under a real monitoring
          visit, it didn't ship.
        </p>
        <p>
          That internal pressure is what turned Purple Directive from a tooling
          effort into a product company. Other sites were running into the same
          problems. The gap between what clinical research software promises and
          what it actually delivers in a small-site context was consistent enough
          to be worth closing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-split-right">
        <div class="milestone-stack">
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>Clinical Operations</strong>
              <span>Phase I-IV study coordination, regulatory submissions, site start-up</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>SOP Library</strong>
              <span>12 SOPs covering the full study lifecycle, aligned to current ICH guidelines</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>CTMS Development</strong>
              <span>Multi-tenant trial management system implementing 21 CFR Part 11 controls</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>AI-Augmented Engineering</strong>
              <span>Integrated AI assistance for document generation, analysis, and compliance automation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section class="section section-tinted">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Founder</h2>
      <p>Founded by Tyrian Murex. Built with AI-augmented engineering by a practitioner currently doing the work — not just advising on it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="founders-grid founders-grid-single">
      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-avatar avatar-tyrian">TM</div>
        <h3>Tyrian Murex</h3>
        <span class="founder-role">Founder &amp; Principal</span>
        <p>
          Clinical research operations, regulatory compliance, and the engineering
          to put both into practice. Currently working on FDA-regulated studies at
          a 21-hospital US academic health system. Background in GCP, ICH E6, and
          site start-up — the daily reality of running studies with lean teams,
          real regulators, and real deadlines. Founded Purple Directive to build
          the tools that didn't exist.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-domains">
          <span>Clinical Ops</span>
          <span>Regulatory</span>
          <span>Engineering</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>What We Build</h2>
      <p>Tools and resources for clinical research sites, sponsors, and the teams who run them.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="products-grid">
      <a href="https://nexrial.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="product-card">
        <strong>Nexrial CTMS</strong>
        <p>Purpose-built trial management for independent research sites. Audit trails, eSource, and ICH E6(R3) controls without enterprise pricing.</p>
        <span class="product-cta">Visit Nexrial →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/sop-bundle" class="product-card">
        <strong>SOP Bundle</strong>
        <p>12 ICH E6(R3)-aligned SOPs covering the full study lifecycle. Ready to adapt and deploy.</p>
        <span class="product-cta">See the SOPs →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/research-report" class="product-card">
        <strong>Research Reports</strong>
        <p>Analyst-grade vendor comparison and regulatory landscape reports for sites making real purchasing decisions.</p>
        <span class="product-cta">View Reports →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/hire" class="product-card">
        <strong>Consulting</strong>
        <p>Site start-up, compliance infrastructure, and regulatory operations support. Engagements scoped by need.</p>
        <span class="product-cta">Work With Us →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Engineering Practices (AI disclosure) -->
  <section class="section section-tinted">
    <div class="engineering-disclosure">
      <p class="engineering-label">Engineering Practices</p>
      <p>
        Purple Directive uses AI-augmented engineering across our software products.
        All code is written and reviewed by Tyrian Murex, with AI assistance used
        internally for development, analysis, and documentation. AI does not act
        as a legal entity, does not sign contracts, and does not represent the
        company in any business or regulatory capacity. Detailed AI engineering
        practices specific to each product are described on that product's site.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Principles -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How We Work</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="principles-grid">
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">01</div>
        <h3>Build What You Use</h3>
        <p>Every product we sell started as an internal tool. The SOP bundle is the same library we use on our own studies. The CTMS runs our own operations. We don't build things we haven't tested on ourselves first.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">02</div>
        <h3>Compliance Is Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>Regulatory compliance isn't a checkbox at the end. It's the foundation everything else is built on. Our software has audit trails, our SOPs reference current ICH guidelines, and our operations are inspection-ready by default.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">03</div>
        <h3>Small Teams, Real Problems</h3>
        <p>We build for organizations running 1-10 studies with lean teams — not 500-person CROs with dedicated IT departments. Our tools are sized for the people who actually need them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">04</div>
        <h3>Ship, Then Improve</h3>
        <p>We'd rather deliver a working tool this week than a perfect tool next quarter. Every product we release gets better based on real use, real monitoring visits, and real feedback from coordinators in the field.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connect -->
  <section class="section section-deep">
    <div class="connect-layout">
      <div>
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Whether you're looking for compliance infrastructure, custom software, or just want to follow along as we build — here's where to find us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="connect-links">
        <a href="/hire" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">
            <!-- chat bubble / work with us -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <strong>Work With Us</strong>
          <span>Consulting, software, partnerships</span>
        </a>
        <a href={social.linkedin.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">
            <!-- linkedin -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
          </span>
          <strong>LinkedIn</strong>
          <span>{social.linkedin.handle}</span>
        </a>
        <a href={social.x.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">
            <!-- X / twitter -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4l16 16M4 20L20 4"/></svg>
          </span>
          <strong>X / Twitter</strong>
          <span>{social.x.handle}</span>
        </a>
        <a href={social.github.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">
            <!-- github -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"/></svg>
          </span>
          <strong>GitHub</strong>
          <span>{social.github.handle}</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #f5f3f8, #ede9fe 45%, #fafafa);
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Origin split */
  .about-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-split-left h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-split-left p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Milestone stack */
  .milestone-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--purple-primary);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .milestone {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .milestone-marker {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--purple-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    position: absolute;
    left: calc(-1 * var(--spacing-lg) - 6px);
  }

  .milestone strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .milestone span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Founders */
  .founders-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .founders-grid-single {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .founder-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--purple-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .founder-avatar {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #4c1d95;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md);
    user-select: none;
  }

  .founder-avatar.avatar-tyrian {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
    border: 3px solid #f59e0b;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #92400e;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .founder-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.2rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .founder-role {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .founder-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
  }

  .founder-domains {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .founder-domains span {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    background: rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.08);
    padding: 0.25em 0.65em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* What We Build (products grid) */
  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .product-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--purple-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .product-card strong {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .product-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .product-cta {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* Engineering disclosure */
  .engineering-disclosure {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .engineering-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .engineering-disclosure p:not(.engineering-label) {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Principles */
  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .principle-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .principle-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }

  .principle-num {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .principle-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .principle-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Connect */
  .connect-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .connect-layout h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .connect-layout > div:first-child p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .connect-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .connect-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .connect-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .connect-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  }

  .connect-card strong {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .connect-card span:last-child {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }

    .about-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .founders-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .products-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .connect-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .connect-links {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
